## Why it matters

This is the first impression the system makes on a new Maxina visitor; the design choices here decide whether someone bounces or commits. Every Maxina member arrives at this screen at some point in their first 30 days — sometimes via the Did You Know guided tour, sometimes by tapping a card on Home, sometimes by asking ORB "show me the legacy profile redirect". Knowing why the screen exists is what stops it from feeling like noise the next time you land here.

## Where to find it

Direct URL: `/profile/:id`. It lives under the **Public** module of the sidebar, on the tab labelled **Legacy Profile Redirect**. If you ask ORB "open the legacy profile redirect" the Navigator will route you straight here.

